{"id":368,"date":"2021-12-27T09:21:00","date_gmt":"2021-12-27T07:21:00","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/?p=368"},"modified":"2022-03-23T21:25:52","modified_gmt":"2022-03-23T19:25:52","slug":"the-future-of-corporate-cloud-banking-a-look-into-things-to-come","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/the-future-of-corporate-cloud-banking-a-look-into-things-to-come\/","title":{"rendered":"The Future of Corporate Cloud Banking. A Look into Things to Come"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>The cloud presents businesses in the <a href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/how-multiple-payment-gateways-help-merchants-sell\/\" data-type=\"post\" data-id=\"182\">payments industry<\/a> with unmatched opportunities. It\u2019s making it easier for banks and other financial institutions to operate affordable service models.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>It offers the payment processors the modernity and agility that is lacking in traditional models.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>New options for banking infrastructure continue to emerge each year thanks to the broad number of deployment options offered by cloud providers and vendors. They include:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Public cloud<\/li><li>Private cloud<\/li><li>Hybrid cloud<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>All this is happening at a time when payments solution providers are undergoing a radical shift.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.insiderintelligence.com\/insights\/financial-services-industry\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">The financial service industry<\/a> has had to reinvent itself as banks focus on maximizing operational efficiency to make them smarter, faster, and easier to use.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Experts in this industry believe that the cloud offers the best route to achieving these goals.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_45 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-grey ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">Table of Contents<\/p>\n<span class=\"e