ive-edge\" title=\"How Payments Solution Companies Can Use the Cloud to Gain a Competitive Edge\">How Payments Solution Companies Can Use the Cloud to Gain a Competitive Edge<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-9\" href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/the-future-of-corporate-cloud-banking-a-look-into-things-to-come\/#prospects-of-the-deployment-of-cloud-technologies-in-the-payments-industry\" title=\"Prospects of the Deployment of Cloud Technologies in the Payments Industry\">Prospects of the Deployment of Cloud Technologies in the Payments Industry<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"the-future-of-corporate-cloud-banking-whats-driving-banks-to-the-cloud\"><\/span>The Future of Corporate Cloud Banking: What\u2019s Driving Banks to the Cloud?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Cloud adoption rates among online payment processors have continued to rise faster than initially anticipated, with studies estimating it will continue to <a href=\"https:\/\/www.siliconrepublic.com\/enterprise\/cloud-computing-predictions-2020\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">grow at a rate of 17%.<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The desire to meet consumer expectations, accelerate financial transactions and simplify IT infrastructure is pushing companies in the payments industry to innovative banking solutions.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>These are solutions that they can deploy quickly and efficiently.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" src=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/I.-Business-Growth-and-Coverage-Expansion.jpg\" alt=\"banking\" class=\"wp-image-427\" srcset=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/I.-Business-Growth-and-Coverage-Expansion.jpg 800w, http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/I.-Business-Growth-and-Coverage-Expansion-300x150.jpg 300w, http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/I.-Business-Growth-and-Coverage-Expansion-768x384.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"open-banking-gathering-pace-due-to-a-new-disruption-era\"><\/span>Open Banking Gathering Pace Due to a New Disruption Era<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The future of corporate cloud Banking looks bright due to the disruption occurring as a result of the <a href=\"https:\/\/www2.deloitte.com\/global\/en\/pages\/financial-services\/articles\/open-banking-around-the-world.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">many open banking and regulations<\/a> getting implemented worldwide.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Challengers have begun to build on their existing market share as corporate clients continue to bank with more than one service provider.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Cloud computing provides payment processors with quick access to multiple platforms to build long-lasting ecosystems.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Depending on their chosen cloud platform, the banks can benefit from access to an open platform that they can use to collaborate and innovate in the digital marketplace.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"what-will-success-in-the-cloud-look-like\"><\/span>What Will Success in The Cloud Look Like?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>When contemplating the future of Corporate cloud Banking, C-suite executives ought to understand that the cloud is among the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.tcs.com\/content\/dam\/tcs\/pdf\/perspectiveapp\/How-the-Cloud-Empowers-Digital-Transformation.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">primary enablers of digital transformation.<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Apart from boosting the capacity of businesses in the payments industry to handle data, it also improves security and business agility.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Cloud enables rapid evolution using on-demand innovation that assists in satisfying the ever-increasing business needs.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The new breed of financial institutions is helping reshape how corporate clients interact with their banking services providers.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Analysts believe that more than <a href=\"https:\/\/tink.com\/blog\/digital-banking-solutions\/what-is-multi-banking\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">50% of corporate clients are multi-banking<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"how-do-will-future-financial-services-look-like-in-the-cloud\"><\/span>How do Will Future Financial Services look Like in the Cloud?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Cloud technologies are attracting increased attention from top managers and IT entrepreneurs. It\u2019s believed that banks will have a completely different outlook in ten years.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Online payment processors need to continue evolving for them to meet the ever-evolving customer expectations. It explains why key figures in the banking industry are continuously talking about the cloud.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"optimization-and-new-coverage\"><\/span>Optimization and New Coverage<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>After considering the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.znetlive.com\/blog\/pros-and-cons-of-cloud-computing\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">pros and cons offered by cloud computing<\/a>, financial experts have divided potential cloud uses into two main categories:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Those that facilitate business development and expansion<\/li><li>Those that boost optimization of the enterprise<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"i-business-growth-and-coverage-expansion\"><\/span>I. Business Growth and Coverage Expansion<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Introducing cloud technology to banking operations will enhance efficiency in the following areas:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>The attraction of new talents. Introducing innovative technologies will allow payments solution providers to attract and utilize the resources linked to specialists such as Scrum Masters, DevOps, and engineers.<\/li><li>Implementation of innovations. Deployment of the cloud will allow for faster testing and implementation of VR, AI, ML, AR, and IoT technologies.<\/li><li>Synchronization of the enterprise. Cloud computing technologies enable different departments in the company to exchange data used in decision-making.<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ii-optimization-of-the-business\"><\/span>II. Optimization of the Business<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The introduction of cloud computing technologies will allow for efficient optimization of internal processes in different areas, such as:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Flexible scaling. Online payment processors can quickly change the total amount of available storage capacity.<\/li><li>Improved IT security. Companies providing cloud services have vast experience in cybersecurity and thus guarantee the implementation of the <a href=\"https:\/\/andersenlab.com\/blueprint\/security-in-the-cloud?utm_source=article&amp;utm_medium=finextra.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">best cybersecurity measures<\/a>.<\/li><li>Better company steadiness. Implementation of cloud technologies will enable the company to become more resilient to typical issues such as power disruptions and cuts.<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" src=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/Open-Banking-Gathering-Pace-Due-to-a-New-Disruption-Era.jpg\" alt=\"banking\" class=\"wp-image-428\" srcset=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/Open-Banking-Gathering-Pace-Due-to-a-New-Disruption-Era.jpg 800w, http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/Open-Banking-Gathering-Pace-Due-to-a-New-Disruption-Era-300x150.jpg 300w, http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/Open-Banking-Gathering-Pace-Due-to-a-New-Disruption-Era-768x384.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"how-payments-solution-companies-can-use-the-cloud-to-gain-a-competitive-edge\"><\/span>How Payments Solution Companies Can Use the Cloud to Gain a Competitive Edge<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Competing in an everchanging financial industry requires access to cloud services and reliance on an excellent cloud-based online payment solution to manage regulatory compliance.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Banks need to excel in three critical areas to compete with other companies in the payments industry. These are:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Convenience: Corporate clients no longer consider convenience based on the number of available branches or operating hours set by a bank. For them, convenience is the ability to complete a financial transaction, e.g., bill payments online.<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<ol start=\"2\"><li>Reputation and trust: Cloud platforms are designed with security in mind. The security features in place help to protect customers against data breaches and phishing attacks. Incorporating built-in mechanisms will provide banks with a payments solution that assists in protecting their reputation and trustworthiness.<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<ol start=\"3\"><li>cost-to-income ratio: The ratio provides an accurate estimate of the kind of success a payment processor will have in the future. The cost-to-income ratio has an impact on all banking operations, from advertising to pricing strategies.<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"prospects-of-the-deployment-of-cloud-technologies-in-the-payments-industry\"><\/span>Prospects of the Deployment of Cloud Technologies in the Payments Industry<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>In the past three to five years, many payments solution businesses have taken steps to help shift their operations to the cloud.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>But as many have come to learn, the transition speed often depends on the involvement level of the IT\/CTO director. They are the main driving force.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.mygreatlearning.com\/blog\/cloud-computing-industry-spend\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Looking at the investments<\/a> happening in the cloud technologies sector, it\u2019s clear that the cloud will soon become a market maker in the tech sector.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>With regard to the financial sphere, payment processors are actively using public, private, and hybrid solutions to develop innovative banking products and solutions.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>The cloud presents businesses in the payments industry with unmatched opportunities. It\u2019s making it easier for banks and other financial institutions to operate affordable service models. It offers the payment processors the modernity and agility that is lacking in traditional models. New options for banking infrastructure continue to emerge each year thanks to the broad [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":426,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[23,16,17],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/368"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=368"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/368\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":429,"href":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/368\/revisions\/429"}],"wp:featu